<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>How to Use MoneyMate</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">

  <!-- Header Section -->
  <header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-blue-500 py-10 text-center text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">How to Use MoneyMate</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl max-w-xl mx-auto">A quick and easy guide to help you manage your transactions effortlessly.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Step-by-Step Guide -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center mb-12">Getting Started with MoneyMate</h2>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">1. Register Your Account</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">To start using MoneyMate, you need to create an account. Click on the <strong>Sign Up</strong> button at the top-right corner of the page and fill in your details. Once registered, you will be able to log in and start tracking your finances.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4">
          <img src="/images/Web/1one.jpg" alt="Register screenshot" class="w-32 h-auto">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">2. Add Customers</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">After logging in, go to the <strong>Customers</strong> section to add individuals or businesses with whom you have financial dealings. You can add as many customers as you like by clicking the <span class="font-bold text-green-600">+</span> button and filling out the required information.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4">
          <img src="/images/Web/2two.jpg" alt="Add customer screenshot" class="w-32 h-auto">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">3. Record Transactions</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Once youâ€™ve added your customers, you can start recording transactions. For each transaction, specify the amount, reason, and date. You can track both money you gave and money you received in real-time.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4">
          <img src="/images/Web/3three.jpg" alt="Record transaction screenshot" class="w-32 h-auto">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">4. Track and View History</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">MoneyMate helps you keep track of your financial interactions by giving you a full history of transactions for each customer. You can easily edit or delete any entry if necessary.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4">
          <img src="/images/Web/4four.jpg" alt="Transaction history screenshot" class="w-32 h-auto">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5 -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">5. Settle Up</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">When it's time to settle up with a customer, MoneyMate will show you the total amount you either owe or are owed. Use this information to ensure transparent and accurate settlements.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4">
          <img src="/images/Web/5five.jpg" alt="Settle up screenshot" class="w-32 h-auto">
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <section class="bg-blue-500 py-12 text-center text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">Start Tracking Your Finances Now</h2>
      <p class="mb-8 text-lg">Manage your transactions and stay on top of your financial obligations with MoneyMate.</p>
      <a href="/customers" class="bg-green-500 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg hover:bg-green-600 transition duration-300">
        Get Started
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="py-6 bg-gray-800 text-center text-white">
    <p>&copy; 2024 MoneyMate. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
